headline: VULCAN ANNOUNCES SECOND QUARTER 2025 CONFERENCE CALL
summary: Vulcan Materials Company (NYSE: VMC) will host its second quarter 2025 earnings conference call on Thursday, July 31, 2025 at 10:00 a.m. CT (11:00 a.m. ET). Financial results will be released before the NYSE market opens.
